### Sign in
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/auth/signin
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "pkay@gmail.com",
  "password": "pkay12345678"
}

### Copy the token from the response JSON `result.token` and paste it into the requests below as the `token` value in the Cookie header (or set a variable named `token`).

### Create Category
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/categories
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: token={{token}}

{
  "name": "Beverage",
  "noe": "drink"
}

### List Categories
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/categories
Cookie: token={{token}}


### Get Category (replace :id)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/categories/:id
Cookie: token={{token}}


### Update Category (replace :id)
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/v1/categories/:id
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: token={{token}}

{
  "name": "Drinks"
}

### Delete Category (replace :id)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/v1/categories/:id
Cookie: token={{token}}


### Create Product
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/products
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: token={{token}}

{
  "name": "Coffee Beans",
  "category": "{{categoryId}}",
  "imageUrl": "http://localhost:3000/upload/coffee.png",
  "costPrice": 10,
  "salePrice": 15
}

### List Products
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/products
Cookie: token={{token}}


### Get Product (replace :id)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/products/:id
Cookie: token={{token}}


### Find Product by Code
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/products/code/:code
Cookie: token={{token}}
